{"word":"G4029 - περίκειμαι - períkeimai - per-ik'-i-mahee - Be bound with","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">περίκειμαι</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">períkeimai</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">per-ik'-i-mahee</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Be bound with</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - கட்டு, கட்டப்படு, சூழ்ந்துகொள்"},{"paragraph":"1. to lie around were hanged"},{"paragraph":"2. passively to be compassed with, have around one"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G4012 - περί - perí - per-ee'/4012\">G4012</a> and <a href=\"#/G2749 - κεῖμαι - keîmai - ki'-mahee/2749\">G2749</a>; to <i>lie</i> all <i>around</i>, that is, <i>inclose</i>, <i>encircle</i>, <i>hamper</i> (literally or figuratively): - be bound (compassed) with, hang about.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G1945/1945\">G1945</a>, <a href=\"#/G2621/2621\">G2621</a>, <a href=\"#/G2749/2749\">G2749</a>, <a href=\"#/G345/345\">G345</a>, <a href=\"#/G3873/3873\">G3873</a>, <a href=\"#/G4029/4029\">G4029</a>, <a href=\"#/G4295/4295\">G4295</a>, <a href=\"#/G480/480\">G480</a>, <a href=\"#/G4873/4873\">G4873</a>, <a href=\"#/G606/606\">G606</a>"}]}